Install
=======

Server configuration
------------

    * Apache
		* mod_rewrite (optional, for pretty URLs)
    * PHP5+
		* php_xsl
		* php_apc (optional, for pretty file upload)
	* MySQL5+ (optional, if you need a database)
	
Installation
------------

    * untar the archive
    * set write access on root directory, for apache
    * install the framework step by step

Details
------------

	* http://redmine.sillysmart.org
doc    * http://www.sillysmart.org